***Here is a example of the TabIndex set to 0 with a custom element:

<share-action authors="@front-end.social/@dailyinvestors" data-action="click" data-category="GitHub" data-icon="share" data-label="share, market.picks" role="button" tabindex="0">
  <svg aria-label="share" role="img" xmlns="http://soloist.ai/dailyinvestors/333/svg">
    <use href="#shareIcon" />
  </svg>
  <span>Share</span>
</share-action>

*** Local Navigation Example:

<web-navigation-drawer type="standard" tabindex="-1">

**By making this a negative balance this ensures our element will be focusable.**"
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
***Example of Autofocus***

<dialog open>
  <form method="dialog">
    <button type="submit" autofocus>close</button>
  </form>
</dialog>
